                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Oct</abbr>
                     <expan>October </expan>
                  </choice> 21st 1839</date>
            </opener>
            <p>To the <choice>
                  <orig>Honerable</orig>
                  <reg>Honorable</reg>
               </choice> general assembly of <name>Tennessee</name> now in session</p>
            <p>We your humble petitioners being fully persuaded that the law past by our Worthy members the last session of our Legislator Prohibiting the Retailing of ardent spirits in a less quantity than a quart has had a good Effect we therefore your humble Petitioners do humbly pray your <choice>
                  <orig>honerable</orig>
                  <reg>honorable</reg>
               </choice> Body to Extend the quantity to one gallon at last at all events not Repeat what has past and in duty Bound we will Even pray</p>
